  "texts": [
    "S 3 consists of three steps.",
    "Initially, a point cloud is generated from the vertices of the original mesh.",
    "Then, a subset of the point cloud is selected based on high values of a user-defined metric.",
    "A sensible metric to investigate temporal fluctuations of turbulent flows is the turbulent kinetic energy (TKE).",
    "Next, a coarse mesh is generated from the reduced point cloud by employing 3D Delaunay triangulation."
  ],
